ement, as you have defined on the Superwall dashboard."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"params","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Optional parameters you’d like to pass with your placement. These can be referenced within the rules"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of your campaign. Keys beginning with "},{"code":"$","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" are reserved for Superwall and will be dropped. Values can be any"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"JSON encodable value, URLs or Dates. Arrays and dictionaries as values are not supported at this time, and will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"be dropped."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"paywallOverrides","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An optional "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/superwall-ios.SuperwallKit\/documentation\/SuperwallKit\/PaywallOverrides","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object whose parameters override the paywall defaults. Use this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to override products and whether it ignores the subscription status. Defaults to "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"onRequestDismiss","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An optional completion block that gets called when the paywall should dismiss. This defaults to "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and the SDK"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"will call "},{"code":"presentationMode.wrappedValue.dismiss()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" by default. Otherwise you must perform the dismissal of the paywall."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"onSkippedView","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A completion block that accepts a "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/superwall-ios.SuperwallKit\/documentation\/SuperwallKit\/PaywallSkippedReason","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and returns an "},{"code":"View","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". This will show"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when the requested paywall is skipped. Defaults to "},{"code":"EmptyView()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"feature","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A completion block containing a feature that you wish to paywall. Access to this block is remotely configurable via the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/superwall.com\/dashboard","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":". If the paywall is set to "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Non Gated","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":", this will be called when"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the paywall is dismissed or if the user is already paying. If the paywall is "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Gated","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":", this will be called only if the user is already paying"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or if they begin paying. If no paywall is configured, this gets called immediately. This will not be called in the event of an error."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This uses ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/superwall-ios.SuperwallKit\/documentation\/SuperwallKit\/Superwall\/getPaywall(forPlacement:params:paywallOverrides:delegate:)","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" under the hood.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"warning","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You’re responsible for the deallocation of this view. If you have a "},{"code":"PaywallView","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" presented somewhere"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and you try to pres